rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Let me play with the
newcomers a bit, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Do you know what the best food
is for the Nopon tribe, mo?

rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0008
rows.name: What a naughty person you are, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0009
rows.name:
There's no way something
like that could be the
best food for Hototo, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0012
rows.name:
Whoops, I won't say any more,
mo. I'd rather not have Hototo's
sanctuary invaded... mo.

rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0014
rows.name:
There's no Nopon in this world who
likes something like that, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350146_01_msg0015
rows.name:
If there were a Nopon who
liked that, their taste
would be just awful, mo.
